{"tid":229873,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"個個都應該損血，但連登仔唔需要損","createTime":"2017-05-05T02:20:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-05T03:41:34.000Z","uid":49197,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"efd329fc143eabcd2d2fdb26a5ac04088ac94131","tid":229873,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T02:20:40.000Z","msg":"損血係一個社會博奕行為黎，如果大家都唔損，咁就會大家都攬炒，呢個道理我唸以大家既智商都會明白，就唔浪費篇幅詳細講解<br />\n<br />\n家下要探討既係以香港既情況，值唔值得連登仔損，扣除大陸蝗搶血問題，其實仲有一個決定性因素影響連登仔應否損血<br />\n<br />\n客觀而言，連登仔通常較少出門，而喺室內活動受傷既機率係遠遠低於室外，故此喺投資/回報角度睇，連登仔損血=蝕底"},{"pid":"de532829dafc43b70f0c4dc2c3a2f9d5c33eb8d1","tid":229873,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T02:21:39.000Z","msg":"吸血鬼 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a091d015e67dd157381f32ec59a0023bc2a7208d","tid":229873,"uid":32786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T02:22:24.000Z","msg":"你損先<br />\n我就唔會捐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n字都未撚識打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"634ef432b0d381c0c2c57b9f72a793255b70fc82","tid":229873,"uid":84447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T02:24:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你損先<br />\n我就唔會捐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n字都未撚識打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n新會然就摺埋打下飛機先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"487bf5b597433f7e1676d7b673376e4b09bd5f7e","tid":229873,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T02:28:06.000Z","msg":"雖然唔關事，但都講下乜野人最需要去損血<br />\n1.已婚人士並計劃以後有bb，需要確保損血個pool長期正常運作唔崩潰<br />\n2.廢老，成日有老人病要輸血<br />\n3.長期户外工作者，遇到危險機會比正常人高好多"},{"pid":"10769fe91c62d4bba6f78e84a771890d5a6aad16","tid":229873,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T02:29:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你損先<br />\n我就唔會捐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n字都未撚識打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有無睇內文，我叫你地唔好損<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋兩登不嬲用損字"},{"pid":"1b9645e4223bd13f659af9b7aa67eea7e9e717b7","tid":229873,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T02:33:46.000Z","msg":"或者改改個題目會清楚d:即使唔計大陸因素，連登仔都唔應該損血，因為回報率真係好低"},{"pid":"ec9e806936ce4bb93e262c6acdce330ff99be9a9","tid":229873,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T02:33:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>或者改改個題目會清楚d:即使唔計大陸蝗因素，連登仔都唔應該損血，因為回報率真係好低</blockquote>"},{"pid":"c309ce35058415b6e1706bc8ca9e723fcbe35c9d","tid":229873,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T02:41:38.000Z","msg":"呢班友咁愛支那人, 佢地身體力行去捐先囉<br />\n十多萬人, 一定夠架喎！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20100605/large/05la1p101.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20100605%2Flarge%2F05la1p101.jpg&h=c34a2fee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c6e9495361872f555576faf01d320288e32b4bd2","tid":229873,"uid":78900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T02:43:52.000Z","msg":"Earnings per blood (EPB) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n識玩一定計回報率, 留返俾D左膠捐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"943b9018c00be755982f055d96a6c3aec82717d8","tid":229873,"uid":24527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T02:47:38.000Z","msg":"如果家人有事，自已即時捐比家人得唔得？"},{"pid":"7cbbcaf3ebb97248043e6f8dd4f40b80570ccfe7","tid":229873,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T03:27:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Earnings per blood (EPB) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n識玩一定計回報率, 留返俾D左膠捐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打識波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd471d6d061de1da72d86cc2d591c0b2c904fc83","tid":229873,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T03:31:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果家人有事，自已即時捐比家人得唔得？</blockquote><br />\n好似得，血同器官都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56fe554fe150836e8650b4eb5e1436bc9063bb70","tid":229873,"uid":51121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T03:33:17.000Z","msg":"其實連登仔根本都唔會去捐血, 又怕死又怕痛又怕蝕底.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n只係多左老人之麻.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14029f6ecd41330bbca2920204b0a976a51060c3","tid":229873,"uid":37798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T03:34:25.000Z","msg":"損血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"896ae33930ffbae97d6d8a4689d93305d87d84c9","tid":229873,"uid":78900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T03:35:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果家人有事，自已即時捐比家人得唔得？</blockquote><br />\n好似得，血同器官都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當社會冇得阻止外來畜牲 (包括南亞狗, 支那畜) 入黎香港影響輸血需求既時侯<br />\n一定唔會捐血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e324d0651cf0622eb23c398587f53032cde9813","tid":229873,"uid":51121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T03:35:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果家人有事，自已即時捐比家人得唔得？</blockquote><br />\n好似得，血同器官都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n要你家人等到最危急個位, 但一般年青人排先, 你家人係老野唔夠血根本唔會上手術枱."},{"pid":"e59acd186d70c7d78f4256b18b42338d85302824","tid":229873,"uid":88029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T03:41:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}